title: Zelda Windwaker HD + Collectors Ed 3 Games Remastered HD for PC
description:
This is a preconfigured install for The Legend of Zelda the Windwaker HD with several HD texture packs, SweetFX, Reshade, and much more.  The various features require very specific emulator versions, settings and plug ins. It can be very complicated to get everything working so I have decided to pack it all up in a release.  This will also install an HD remastered  The Legend of Zelda Collectors Edition which features HD remassterd copies of The Legend Of Zelda Ocarina of Time, and The Legend of Zelda Majora's Mask.

3 full Zelda games completely remastered in HD for PC, and there is no better way to experience these games!


Just install and run the game exe file just like any other PC game.  The emulator, and all game specific settings have all been wrapped in the games exe and install for easy install and use.



Configured to use a standard PC controller (xbox360, etc)
